As a traveling student, I mentioned to Florence that the next door neighbor was ridiculously loud, waking me up several days at 1:30 Am when I have to be up at 3:00Am. We then agreed setting up quiet hours so future guests may get some rest. I personally tried to talk to the incredibly rude neighbor several times, however she did not care. I would as a word of warning for any future hosts, highly NOT recommend her as a guest in your home. After my stay, I would recommend this airbnb for anyone visiting DE.
